title: Executive Order 5895-Revocation of Withdrawal of Public Lands Pending Resurvey, Florida
content: It is hereby ordered that Executive Order No. 5030, dated January 18, 1929, which withdrew the public lands in Tps. 14 and 15 S., R. 25 E., Tallahassee meridian, Florida, pending resurvey, be, and the same is hereby, revoked.
citation: Herbert Hoover, Executive Order 5895-Revocation of Withdrawal of Public Lands Pending Resurvey, Florida Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/361479
